Won't be coming here again  I am a young teen I've been to this place before as it is in my neighborhood and today I went and ordered Fried Chicken Gizzards which cost 4 dollars and 50 cents. Being familiar with the place I payed prior to ordering (which is arguably a bad decision) and when I did receive the order was told I hadn't payed for the product which I had. I had argued my point with multiple employees for a number of minutes and was still told that I hadn't payed for an order that I rightfully did. After arguing for some time and leaving and returning with my parents for extra support and the workers finally actually checking the camera after nonchalantly glancing at the security tape they would not even so much as apologize for the "inconvenience" if I could call it that. Thankfully had my money refunded to me but the experience completely ruined both my appetite and my day.
